Using Synergy 1.4, it's easy to send us your log for when we need debug info about your problem.


First, turn up the logging to "Debug2". Go to '''Edit''' > '''Settings''' > '''Logging'''. Select '''Debug2''' from the '''Logging level''' drop down and then click '''OK'''.

[[File:LogLevelDebug2.png]]


Then click '''Apply''', or '''Stop''' and then '''Start''' if using desktop mode.

[[File:ApplyHighlight.png]]


Right click the log output area and click '''Select All''' then '''Copy'''. Paste your results on [http://pastebin.com/ Pastebin] and send us the link!
